Dialogue: 1,0:03:22.37,0:03:24.54,Default,,0,0,0,,我們還以為你走了
Dialogue: 1,0:03:24.57,0:03:25.84,Default,,0,0,0,,你這是怎麼了？
Dialogue: 1,0:03:25.87,0:03:28.01,Default,,0,0,0,,呃
Dialogue: 1,0:03:28.04,0:03:30.54,Default,,0,0,0,,克羅伊，你這樣子太慘了
Dialogue: 1,0:03:30.58,0:03:32.81,Default,,0,0,0,,沒事吧？
Dialogue: 1,0:03:38.05,0:03:40.75,Default,,0,0,0,,三天？
Dialogue: 1,0:03:45.16,0:03:47.53,Default,,0,0,0,,你到底去了哪裏？
