Dialogue: 1,0:03:53.16,0:03:53.90,Default,,0,0,0,,啥？
Dialogue: 1,0:03:55.13,0:03:56.53,Default,,0,0,0,,呃
Dialogue: 1,0:03:56.57,0:03:58.54,Default,,0,0,0,,他們把我抓走的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.21,0:04:02.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn方正大黑繁体\fad(500,500)\fs50\be25\fsp5\bord2\shad2\c&HB6E1F7&\3c&H102D78&\4c&H00195F&\pos(225,450)}翻译  lydia萌
Dialogue: 1,0:03:58.57,0:04:00.37,Default,,0,0,0,,我當時自己在運送補給
Dialogue: 1,0:04:00.41,0:04:02.64,Default,,0,0,0,,大意了，對不起
